Server Management:

We reserve the right to view, edit, or remove servers from our system if they violate our terms.
Creating, posting, or hosting servers with inappropriate content is strictly prohibited and may result in the suspension of your account for a duration determined by the severity of the violation.

Account Suspension for Moderated Servers:

Users found in servers moderated by us may face account suspension based on the content within the server, with the duration varying depending on the nature of the violation.

Message Monitoring:

We retain the right to view or remove messages that violate our terms to ensure a safe and enjoyable environment for all users.

Compliance with Roblox's Terms of Service:

Users are reminded not to post anything that goes against Roblox's Terms of Service. Violations may result in account consequences as outlined by Roblox.
